quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  8,53,"Nokuda kwekuti Allah havashanduri chipo chavakapa vanhu kusvikira vashandura zviri mavari. Uye zvirokwazvo, Allah vanonzwa zvose, vanoziva zvose"
  8,54,"Kufanana nehunhu hwevanhu vaFarawo, uye hweavo mushure mavo. Vakaramba humboo hwaTenzi vavo. Naizvozvo takavaparadza nokuda kwezvitadzo zvavo. Uye takanyudza vanhu vaFarawo nokuti vose vaive vatadzi"
  8,55,"Zvirokwazvo, zvisikwa (zvinorarama) zvakashata pamberi paAllah ndeavo vasingatendi; nokudaro havazombotendi"
  8,56,"Ndeavo vawakapana chitsidzirano navo, asi vanoputsa chitsidzirano nguva nenguva, uye havatyi Allah"
  8,57,"Naizvozvo kana mavakurira muhondo, vapei mutongo wakaoma kuti mudzinganise avo vanovatevera, (uye) kuti vatore chidzidzo"
  8,58,"Kana uchitya (Muhammad (SAW)) kubiridzirwa (kunyengedzwa) kubva kune vanhu vapi zvavo, vadzosere (chitsidzo chavo) pane kuenzana pakati penyu (kuti pasave nechimwe chitsidzo pakati pako navo). Zvirokwazvo, Allah havadi avo vanobiridzira (vanonyengedza)"
  8,59,"Uye zvirokwazvo, avo vasingatendi vasafunge kuti vanokwanisa kutiza (mutongo hwaAllah). Chokwadi, havambokwanisi kuzvidzivirira (kubva kumutongo hwaAllah)"
  8,60,"Uye vagadzirirei hondo yakasimba kusanganisira mabhiza ehondo (zvombo zvehondo, pfuti, ndege, motokari nezvimwe zvakadaro) kuti mutyise nazvo vavengi vaAllah uye nemi, uye neavo vamusingazivi vasiri pakati pavo, asi vachizivikanwa naAllah. Uye chingava chipi chamunoshandisa munzira yaAllah chichabhadharwa kwamuri, uye hamuzombodzvanyirirwi"
  8,61,"Asi kana vachida runyararo munofanirwa kuita saizvozvo, uye movimba naAllah. Zvirokwazvo, (Allah) ndivo vanonzwa zvese, uye vanoziva zvese"